item.title: Tokyo University see away indisciplined Ninjas
item.author: Joseph Brown,
item.description: Tokyo University 1st XV 32 ICURFC 1st XV 7 The second game day of the IC Ninja’s tour of Japan began a much like the first. Weary, hungover bodies dragged themselves across the whitewash, expectant. Unfortunately, the similarities end here. With two play makers, Brown and Chalke, injured as well as …
